		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I only used single screen mirroring in order to scroll 8-ways and have the statusbar on the second name table.
<br />
<br />I remember reading a thread about simulating single screen mirroring with either H or V mirroring, (not sure, can't find it at the moment) so I can try and modify it to use one of those.
<br />
<br />So what type is the mirroring going to be hardwired to?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
