	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm accepting new programs and taking suggestions on what to pick up..
<br />
<br />I moved to a bigger ROM and simpler mapper (32kB banks).  This also means I have more ROM space that's free, so I'm hoping some of you have some demos or something you'd like to see on the cartridge.  Or even another game.  There will be 100kB - 200kB free, lots of space.  If I don't fill it all soon I'll be burning it blank because I need to get this cart done.
<br />
<br />Also I wonder if anyone has any decent text compression for NES that's already developed.  And better compression for CHR besides RLE.

		

		</td>
